node.title: Man dies at North Island's most southern point, Cape Palliser
node.description: A man has died following a water-related incident at Cape Palliser, police said on Friday.
node.content: ["A man has died following a water-related incident at Cape Palliser, police said on Friday.", "The incident happened just after 9am.", "Police are making enquiries.", "Cape Palliser is the southernmost point of the North Island, considerably further south than Blenheim, Picton and Nelson in the South Island.\u00a0"]
